<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: sans-serif;
        color: #eeeeee;
        background-color: #2d2e32;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .container {
        width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #2d2e32;
        padding-top: 60px;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo img {
        height: 40px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .link {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 30px;
        color: #52b9ff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      hr {
        border-color: whitesmoke;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .confirm-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-end;
      }

      .confirm {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 120px;
        margin: 40px 0;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 12px 24px !important;
        color: #444444;
        font-weight: bold;
        background: #00eaaf;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          #fa7900 0%,
          #df36b4 43%,
          #0063ea 77%,
          #00eaaf 100%
        );
        border: 0px solid white;
      }

      .footer p {
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .footer .social {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .footer .social a {
        margin-right: 20px;
      }

      .footer .visit {
        color: #eeeeee;
        font-size: 13px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="<%= httpsUrl %>/logo.png" />
      </div>
      <p>Congrats <%= userName %></p>
      <p>
        You have won
        <a href="<%= artworkUrl %>"><%= artworkTitle %></a> with your bid of <%=
        bidAmount %>!
      </p>
      <p>
        If an NFT, the token will be delivered to your <%= projectName %> wallet
        and displayed under your Collection tab on your profile page.
      </p>
      <p>
        If the artwork also has a physical piece, the artist will reach out to
        you shortly through email or the socials you have provided on your
        profile page. You can also join the
        <a href="<%= telegramUrl %>"><%= projectName %> Telegram</a>, where most
        of our artist community congregates, and odds are, you can get in touch
        with them there!
      </p>
      <p>Good luck with your future auctions!</p>
      <p>Best, <br /><%= projectName %> Team</p>
      <hr />
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Follow Us</p>
        <div class="social">
          <a href="<%= twitterUrl %>">
            <img style="width: 20px" src="<%= httpsUrl %>/twitter.png" />
          </a>
          <a href="<%= telegramUrl %>">
            <img style="width: 20px" src="<%= httpsUrl %>/telegram.png" />
          </a>
        </div>
        <a class="visit" href="<%= httpsUrl %>">Visit website</a>
        <p>Â© <%= projectName %> <%= new Date().getFullYear() %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
